Police are investigating the death of a man whose body was found in a trench. The body had marks on the neck and back. It was not clear whether the man had been attacked or was the victim of the current heavy rains in the city. ALSO READ:

Fury as body of missing girl found in tank Police said they were informed about the discovery of the body in Dagoretti. In Buru Buru, police said they were investigating the death of a seven-year-old girl whose body was found in a trench. She had been reported missing from Salange area. Those looking for her found her body on Saturday.